{"tid":647928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿富汗連環炸彈襲擊增至最少25死　包括記者及警察","createTime":"2018-04-30T09:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T09:07:45.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d77fcc8d2b68fcde7f79f20e3a628c795f0fb5d","tid":647928,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:07:00.000Z","msg":"阿富汗早上發生的連環自殺式炸彈襲擊，增至最少25人死亡，45人受傷。極端組織「伊斯蘭國」透過旗下通訊社承認責任，表示襲擊是以設在首都喀布爾的情報機關總部為目標。<br />\n<br />\n法新社證實他們一名攝影記者在襲擊中喪生。阿富汗內政部發言人說，8名記者及4名警員喪生。<br />\n<br />\n襲擊涉及兩宗爆炸，一名電單車駕駛者引爆身上炸彈，15分鐘之後，現場發生第2次爆炸，警方說是針對到場採訪首宗爆炸案的記者及圍觀的民眾。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1393942-20180430.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1393942-20180430.htm&d=2a7ilcOh5yBi5M4PnETHkwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=20153e61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1393942-20180430.htm&h=0e77743e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1393942-20180430.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d56e9a094e950276fceb09e90124de9f397407be","tid":647928,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"幾時到中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}